AD_TAB.NAME: Price Rule Version
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.relatedProduct is null and e.relatedProductCategory is null

AD_TAB.NAME: Purchasing
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define information necessary to purchase this product from a specific vendor.
AD_TAB.HELP: Purchasing tab information is used for products that are planned by the purchasing plan.

AD_TAB.NAME: Modify Taxes Categories
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Defines taxes modification for products linked to service
AD_TAB.HELP: Defines taxes modification for products linked to service. Products linked to this service that belongs to the configured category will change the tax category when linked to this service.

AD_TAB.NAME: Characteristic Configuration
AD_TAB.HELP: Characteristic Configuration tab contains the available values for each characteristic assigned to the generic product. Price modifiers to create the variants are defined in this tab as well.

AD_TAB.NAME: Characteristics
AD_TAB.HELP: Relation of characteristics assigned to the Product

AD_TAB.NAME: Accounting
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Create and edit G/L accounts to be used in transactions including a selected product.
AD_TAB.HELP: Accounting tab allows to configure the ledger accounts to be used while posting product related transactions such as product purchase or sales to the general ledger.

AD_TAB.NAME: Translation
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Edit your product name translations for the predefined languages of your choice.
AD_TAB.HELP: Product names can be translated to any language.

AD_TAB.NAME: Substitute
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define substitute products to be used if this product becomes unavailable.
AD_TAB.HELP: Define substitute products to be used if this product becomes unavailable.

AD_TAB.NAME: Product
AD_TAB.HELP: Product window allows the creation of items such as products, raw materials, resources, services, etc.

AD_TAB.NAME: Price
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define prices which will be used to buy or sell this product.
AD_TAB.HELP: A product can be part of many Price List Versions which are valid for a given time period.

AD_TAB.NAME: Costing
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define cost information for this specific product.
AD_TAB.HELP: Costing tab collects and summarize product cost related information as a result of every product transaction. Product's costs are valid during a fixed date range and can be calculated either by using an Average or a Standard costing algorithm.

AD_TAB.NAME: Products
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Products included/excluded in a Service Product
AD_TAB.HELP: The user can define if a product can be related to a product of 'Service' type by creating a relation between an Order Line of the Service product and another Sales Order Line of the product included/excluded.

AD_TAB.NAME: Stock
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: This Tab shows the available Stock for this Product in the application. It only shows Storage Bins for which the quantity available of the Product is not 0
AD_TAB.HELP: This Tab shows the available Stock for this Product in the application. It only shows Storage Bins for which the quantity available of the Product is not 0
AD_TAB.WHERECLAUSE: qtyonhand <> 0 AND qtyorderonhand <> 0 AND reservedqty <> 0 AND allocatedqty <> 0
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.quantityOnHand <> 0 or e.onHandOrderQuanity <> 0 or e.reservedQty <> 0 or e.allocatedQuantity <> 0

AD_TAB.NAME: Product Categories
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Product Categories included/excluded in a Service Product
AD_TAB.HELP: The user can define if a product of a certain product category can be related to a product of 'Service' type by creating a relation between an Order Line of the Service product and another Sales Order Line of the product belonging to included/excluded product categories.

AD_TAB.NAME: Bill of Materials
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Edit the bill of materials components the selected product consists of.
AD_TAB.HELP: This tab allows to edit the bill of materials components the selected product consists of.

AD_TAB.NAME: Costing Rule
AD_TAB.HELP: Costing rule tab allows to review the costing rules that apply to the product within a given date range.

AD_TAB.NAME: Transactions
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Transaction tab is a summarized view of all the transactions of a product.
AD_TAB.HELP: Transaction tab is a summarized view of all the transactions of a product.

AD_TAB.NAME: UOM
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Add a unit of measurement to this product.
AD_TAB.HELP: Add a unit of measurement to this product.

AD_TAB.NAME: Manufacturing
AD_TAB.DESCRIPTION: Define specific characteristics which allow this product to be used in an organization.
AD_TAB.HELP: Manufacturing tab is used for products that are planned by the manufacturing plan.
